Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,「空气」这种行为就不再仅仅是惯用句了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,居然要实际操作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,受教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,花…小花名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 受教了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得不是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小冠 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子很擅长让猫亲近自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是猫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小冠也超级粘荣依子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个 对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
